2026-04-28T18:18:00.2337496Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2338539Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2339570Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2340605Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2341634Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2342661Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-28T18:18:00.2343693Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
