2026-04-28T18:18:00.4217743Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-28T18:18:00.4218089Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-28T18:18:00.4218431Z 30        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-28T18:18:00.4218727Z 31        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
